    "description": "Make your way towards the tower, but beware of dangerous traps and enemies hidden behind any corner! As you progress through the game, don't forget to collect gems to purchase upgrades from Burlar's Bazaar!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><u>Climb!</u></strong></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321700/extras/f02001e870cfbed902498b07b04f7aa6.poster.avif?t=1762460632\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321700/extras/f02001e870cfbed902498b07b04f7aa6.webm?t=1762460632\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321700/extras/f02001e870cfbed902498b07b04f7aa6.mp4?t=1762460632\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Climb up the tower and discover more of the treasures that lie within it!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><u>Charge Jump!</u></strong></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321700/extras/663e2892f7ff387cd3999d445f96bab8.poster.avif?t=1762460632\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321700/extras/663e2892f7ff387cd3999d445f96bab8.webm?t=1762460632\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321700/extras/663e2892f7ff387cd3999d445f96bab8.mp4?t=1762460632\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Use your Charge Jump to jump long distances, however once you release the jump key you'll be left with no air control! <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><u>Grapple!</u></strong></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321700/extras/d233c9f6bbe17b0c537908f3eaac0625.poster.avif?t=1762460632\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321700/extras/d233c9f6bbe17b0c537908f3eaac0625.webm?t=1762460632\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321700/extras/d233c9f6bbe17b0c537908f3eaac0625.mp4?t=1762460632\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Equip your grapple hook to reach higher locations!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><u>Grenades!</u></strong></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321700/extras/b67900f4c407f8b12ff7307e117c6482.poster.avif?t=1762460632\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321700/extras/b67900f4c407f8b12ff7307e117c6482.webm?t=1762460632\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321700/extras/b67900f4c407f8b12ff7307e117c6482.mp4?t=1762460632\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You can use your grenades to break through wooden doors, perhaps you will find hidden areas!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><u>Shovel Donk!</u></strong></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321700/extras/58c6d1e1b6d842fbbec52e7824fba0e4.poster.avif?t=1762460632\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321700/extras/58c6d1e1b6d842fbbec52e7824fba0e4.webm?t=1762460632\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321700/extras/58c6d1e1b6d842fbbec52e7824fba0e4.mp4?t=1762460632\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Use your trusty shovel to destroy boxes or defend yourself against enemies!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><u>Hazards!</u></strong></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321700/extras/7b8eebf1c56342591059ad28b22d3b80.poster.avif?t=1762460632\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321700/extras/7b8eebf1c56342591059ad28b22d3b80.webm?t=1762460632\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321700/extras/7b8eebf1c56342591059ad28b22d3b80.mp4?t=1762460632\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Beware of hazards and traps that try to stop you from traversing the tower!",
